Package: sirad
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Calculating Daily Solar Radiation and Evapotranspiration
Version: 2.2-1
Date: 2014-12-13
Author: Jedrzej S. Bojanowski
Maintainer: Jedrzej S. Bojanowski <jedrzej.bojanowski@gmail.com>
Description: Sirad package provides functions for: (1) calculating daily global solar radiation at horizontal surface using several well-known models (i.e. Angstrom-Prescott, Supit-Van Kappel, Hargreaves, Bristow and Campbell, and Mahmood-Hubbard), (2) model calibration based on ground-truth data, and (3) model auto-calibration. The FAO Penmann-Monteith equation to calculate evapotranspiration is also included.
URL: http://sirad.r-forge.r-project.org/, http://mars.jrc.ec.europa.eu/mars/Projects/Solar-Radiation-in-MCYFS, http://jbojanowski.pl 
Imports: zoo, ncdf, raster
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
